channel.title: Only people on my router can log in?
channel.description:
okay so my friends try to log onto my private server and they cant. but my home computer and my laptop under my router can. idk why. i portforwarded and stuff
i port forwarded correctly im pretty sure
anyone through my router can connect to my server but other people cant.
im not sure why ive report forwarded and all that shiz

item.title: Only people on my router can log in?
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

Yea, this means it has an in-coming firewall. That, or your no-ip was made from the wrong address, if your using one.
